enhanced_by.reason: The entrySet method relies on the composite maps added via addComposited to generate the set of entries.
Removing a map from the composite affects the set of entries returned by entrySet.
Clearing the composite maps affects the set of entries returned by entrySet.
Adding or updating entries in the composite maps affects the set of entries returned by entrySet.
Removing entries from the composite maps affects the set of entries returned by entrySet.
